# Styling Rules — Dieter Rams / Braun Aesthetic

## Tailwind CSS v4
- All design tokens are in `@theme` in `app/assets/css/main.css`. There is NO `tailwind.config.js`.
- Use semantic token classes: `bg-bg-primary`, `text-text-secondary`, `border-border-default`, `text-accent`.
- Gradient syntax: `bg-linear-to-r` (NOT `bg-gradient-to-r` — Tailwind v4 change).
- To add new tokens, add them to `@theme` in `main.css`.

## Design Constraints
- Colors: Warm neutrals only. Accent `#D4600C` is for primary actions only.
- Border radius: 4px default (`rounded-md`). Never use 16px+ or bubbly corners.
- Shadows: Warm-tinted, minimal (`--shadow-xs` at rest). No colored shadows.
- Motion: 100ms hover, 200ms expand, 350ms page. No spring/bounce easing.
- Typography: Inter font. Lowercase nav labels. Sentence case headings.
- Icons: Phosphor Icons (light, 1.5px stroke, 20px). `currentColor` only.

## Forbidden
- No inline `style="..."` attributes.
- No cool blue-greys or pure `#808080` greys.
- No Tailwind default palette colors (`bg-red-500`, `text-blue-400`).
- No `rounded-full` on containers (pills/avatars only).
- No emoji as icons.
